data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the prestigious Quiet Creek community . This magnificent four bedroom three bath residence  is an entertainer's Paradise! This greenbelt lot boasts a spacious yard with  a custom waterfall pool and jacuzzi making   living here feel like vacation everyday!   The upstairs game room/theatre room is a must have as well when entertaining guests. The master bedroom and mother in law suite with their  own private restrooms are all located on the first floor. And, lastly, this gem of a home is located in a cul de sac with no neighbors to your right for plenty of privacy. This home boasts numerous amenities and features that cater to comfort and entertainment.  Convenient access to 1604, 35 and I 10 near RAFB.   Don't miss your chance to fall in love with this dream home and Experience the epitome of comfort and entertainment at 10111 Shallow Bank.
